Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.66,0:00:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃瀨老師\N黃瀨老師在嗎，黃瀨老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼，原來是久米原老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是感冒請假嗎？\N為何這時候會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃瀨老師請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經有超過100名\N學生成為你的犧牲品了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就釋放學生們\N離開那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你的要求是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你需要人質
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.23,0:00:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我，身為老師的我\N願意代替學生們去當人質
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽見沒，多廉價的台詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爆笑了，笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也，你有行動電話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久米原老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上城，村野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧\N只有你們被釋放出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨，久米原老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃瀨老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才妳那充滿勇氣的發言\N我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我可不是白痴\N你真以為我會中你的圈套嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會是圈套？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是圈套的話，妳就來證明一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,証明？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對，先脫光妳穿的所有衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保證你沒有\N帶竊聽器等可疑物品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辦不到嗎？\N原來剛才妳說的話是騙人的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放心了，原來老師也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最愛的還是自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:02:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，我願意脫光衣服\N可是你要保證不傷害學生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一樣是脫\N我就為妳打燈光好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警官們也好好欣賞一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止是沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來檢查內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也，拜託你，別再...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些就是全部嗎？老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時先放你一馬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久米原老師來吧，我等著妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我，在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還用說\N就是大家所在的科學教室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這，這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳來得正好，久米原老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃瀨老師，你對這些孩子們\N做了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別不說話呀，到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也，竊聽器的檢查\N還不夠完全吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家說想幫忙檢查老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續剛才的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大家開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要......！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手...不要...不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師的乳房很大，要調查挺辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也你這樣檢查不詳細喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滴乳了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是特意體質吧\N還是避孕藥吃的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是由模擬懷孕狀態\N來抑制排卵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說偶爾也會有這種例子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃太多要是不好的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想擠擠看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就擠擠看吧，光也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說奶儲存太多不擠出來\N乳房會脹痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有脹痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N女人興奮時乳房會脹起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽爸爸說過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手，求求你，別再折磨我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得有人幫妳擠\N妳可要好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳房脹了許多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧，老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦，出來呀，好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師妳合作點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這種滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃喔，老師，妳的乳房好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的，不檢查竊聽器啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最後一根了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好吧，你的傷沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧，沒有流血呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起\N過去我一直欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天更改預定節目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,播報現在仍未解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵學園挾持師生事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖教師黃瀨的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媒體已經在吵鬧了，無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本節目探尋黃瀨這個人的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到一位可靠人士提供了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:08:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是本案關鍵人物的女性照片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請看，這位女性就是黃瀨的親姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她本來也是教師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為與學生有不純異姓交往...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得她，她是個淫亂教師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勾引男學生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還同時玩弄幾個男學生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太驚人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後來這個事件被發現\N它被學校解聘，還被取消老師執照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是應當的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在那之後的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個說法她可能是被輪姦的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐，妳要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐，妳要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐，姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們別再胡說了！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你們，就是你們逼死姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我姐就是你們害死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是被殺死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被好事的新聞媒體警察與無知\N的大眾還有這世間的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些聖職者\N滿口虛偽的仁義道德算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點小事就加以責難
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論警察，媒體\N還有你們這些板著被害者面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無知又愚蠢的大眾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本沒有人要知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原諒，不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉彥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是太驚人了\N妳的氣質與我姐姐有些像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃瀨，黃瀨吉彥，聽見沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎樣了\N久米原老師怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人質们都平安無事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答呀，黃瀨吉彥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼，原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才知道我的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣，我就不客氣了\N拿你當實驗動物好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你別太過分了，黃瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔，村野，你是突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此，原來這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村野，我就看看你有多少覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到屋頂在媒體面前\N跟小悠作愛好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼，不願意嗎\N我覺得村野應該會很滿意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法，光也\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你代替村野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下\N小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我，我願意跟直人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:12:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠，真的好嗎？\N真的願意跟我做愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直人，我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠，妳很美，太美了，小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭\N妳很美喔，小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像在作夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與你這樣子...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美了\N討厭，好丟臉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮喔，小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡...討厭...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠，要去了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直人，我...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直人，直人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幹什麼，噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有攝影機在拍\N你們還像禽獸一樣亂叫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了，你們喜歡被看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人看就熱情不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來這樣，所以才這樣緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你們那麼喜歡被看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次就跟我一起讓大家看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，直人，直人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來，讓大家看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手，不准對小悠下手，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要讓你知道我比直人好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託，住手，我怎樣都無所謂\N別再欺負小悠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己享受過了\N現在說那個沒意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧，小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠的那裡真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱熱的，太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，我要射了，射了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼\N我一個人享受是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該讓大家也上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對，讓大家看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這，這裡是現場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來應該是人質的男學生們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然圍起來欺負一個女學生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在完全無法知道內情了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，不要，不要呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手，不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手，你們別欺負姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活該，他們都死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐，我成功了，我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，剩下來的你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就用網路來做一回奴隸販賣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網路市場開始拍賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也，你去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂，你拿攝影機拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要透過網路做現場轉播
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓後舉辦票選活動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這裡誰最性感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了，老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡，裡面到底怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警官，糟了，你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭，大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也，來吧，光也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本井，你...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從以前就喜歡你了，光也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了，為何像小孩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想聽人說喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是從母親過世後\N再也沒有人說喜歡我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒問題了\N有我在不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本井，我做了那麼\N過分的事妳還...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係，因為我就是\N忍不住喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就是十萬人次了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，網站真是太容易經營了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這，這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也，叫大家快放棄這蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本井，我的本井
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼，為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:22:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你門這些人還算是人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你們沒有\N身為人的尊嚴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了，我要讓一切結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手，吉彥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼可能，難道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉彥，讓事情結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐，真的是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐，我好想見妳，姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉彥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼妳要死掉，姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拋下我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼，為什麼妳要死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.23,0:22:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，讓你孤單一人\N讓你寂寞，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.06,0:22:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐，姐姐，姐姐———
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在看著你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後也是，你再也不孤單了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.56,0:23:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐，我照你說的做了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了炸彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.00,0:23:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照妳的信說的做了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才來這裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.26,0:23:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向欺負姐姐的人報仇了\N所以，所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.73,0:23:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我，是我寄信的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.06,0:23:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我很無聊，一個人孤孤單單的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.73,0:23:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如爸爸所說的\N讀書進好學校當個醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣活下去也很無聊\N所以我想要死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.23,0:23:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才騙老師做炸彈，所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:23:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你現在不孤單了\N我不會讓你寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，現在起你得贖罪才行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是為了你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人是有兩次生命的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.30,0:24:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次是活著時的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.03,0:24:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次是在大家的回憶中的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.10,0:24:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是永恆不變的，只要大家沒忘記\N就可以永遠的活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.76,0:24:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是好事或是壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.86,0:24:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢...明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.36,0:24:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了，姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.33,0:25:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.16,0:25:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.53,0:25:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭大家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.23,0:25:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個來爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.86,0:25:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把...討厭的東西...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.46,0:25:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.43,0:25:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起炸死
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.30,0:25:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放下那個東西，由紀子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,